  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3, partial assessment)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. Model Risk Level is set to 3, reflecting moderate model influence and decision consequence. Ten of thirteen credibility factors have been assessed; three factors — Model form, Model inputs, and Equivalency of input parameters — are flagged as beyond the current assessment scope and carry factorStatus not-assessed. The rationale for exclusion references resource constraints and deferred analysis without providing concrete justification for why these factors are immaterial at MRL 3. Decision is recorded as Accepted despite the unassessed factors.",
